These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: epic, musical
Sport: rowing, tennis
1. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left of Sport:rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Sport     | tennis | rowing  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
